        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利據悉擬借助信用風險轉移市場 降低對AI數據中心的風險敞口",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 作為給人工智能競賽提供融資的關鍵參與者之一，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根士丹利\">摩根士丹利</a>正在考慮通過所謂的重大風險轉移(SRT)來降低其對部分數據中心的風險敞口。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士透露，該銀行已與潛在投資者就一項與AI基礎設施相關企業貸款組合掛鉤的SRT計畫進行了初步洽談。由於信息尚未公開，知情人士要求匿名。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以數據中心風險敞口為支撐的SRT，仍是信用風險轉移市場的一個新生代領域。在信用風險轉移市場中，銀行通過向機構投資者出售信用掛鉤證券來對沖信用風險敞口、管理資本充足率、釋放資產負債表空間。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2587e2e0-e430-319d-a471-69d1ae28bab0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示，摩根士丹利也在探索其他方式來對沖或銀團化部分數據中心敞口，而且目前尚無法保證早期階段的SRT談判最終會達成協議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利的代表不予置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Morgan Stanley Sounds Out Investors for SRT Tied to Data Centers</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%93%AC%E5%80%9F%E5%8A%A9%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E8%BD%89%E7%A7%BB%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%B0%8Dai%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E6%95%9E%E5%8F%A3-004736565.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 09:20:52",
